### UI Tab

#### [NEW] [cookie_tab.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/cookie_tab.py)

**Layout** (similar to AZ-Labs screenshot):
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ 🍪 Cookie Manager                               │
├──┬──────────────┬───────┬──────────┬──────┬──────┤
│# │ EMAIL        │ PROXY │LAST LOGIN│STATUS│ACTION│
├──┼──────────────┼───────┼──────────┼──────┼──────┤
│1 │ user@gmail   │ —     │03-20     │🟢Live│🔑Login│
│2 │ acc2@gmail   │ ip:p  │03-19     │🔴Dead│🔑Login│
├──┴──────────────┴───────┴──────────┴──────┴──────┤
│ + ADD ACCOUNT                                    │
│ Email: [___________] Proxy: [___________] [+Add] │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│[Extract Chrome][Login All][Check All][Refresh]   │
│[Bulk Import]  [Remove Selected]                  │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Buttons:**
- **Extract Chrome** — Extract cookies from Chrome browser directly
- **🔑 Login** (per row) — Open Selenium browser for that account
- **Login All** — Sequential login for all accounts
- **Check All** — Test all cookie files, update status
- **Refresh** — Re-login dead accounts
- **Bulk Import** — Import cookies.txt files
- **Remove Selected** — Right-click or button to remove

